╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║  KAYNAKLAR:
║    fence_ipmi_<node>      - STONITH (IPMI/iDRAC/iLO)
║    dlm-clone              - DLM (Her 2 Node)
║    lvmlockd-clone         - LVM Locking (Her 2 Node)
║    gfs2_lv_activate-clone - GFS2 LV (Her 2 Node)
║    gfs2_fs-clone          - GFS2 Filesystem (Her 2 Node)
║    gfs2_health-clone      - GFS2 I/O Sağlık Denetçisi (Her 2 Node, 15s)
║    php-fpm-clone          - PHP-FPM (Her 2 Node)
║    nginx-clone            - Nginx Web Sunucu (Her 2 Node)
║    pgsql_lv_activate      - pgsql LV (Sadece Aktif Node)
║    pgsql_fs               - pgsql Filesystem (Sadece Aktif Node)
║    vip                    - Virtual IP (Sadece Aktif Node)
║    postgresql             - PostgreSQL (Sadece Aktif Node)
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║  KAYNAK SIRALAMA (Doğru sıra):
║    dlm-clone → lvmlockd-clone → gfs2_lv_activate-clone → gfs2_fs-clone
║    lvmlockd-clone → pgsql_lv_activate → pgsql_fs → postgresql
║    gfs2_fs-clone + postgresql → php-fpm-clone → nginx-clone
║    (php-fpm ve nginx EN SON iki kaynak)
║    Colocation: postgresql + pgsql_fs + pgsql_lv_activate ↔ vip
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║  KONTROL KOMUTLARI:
